  Beng5-ki5-jian5, chit e5 un7-tong7 si7 tui3 nng7 ui7 hian2-tu3 e5 jin5-but8 lai5 khai-si2--e5, nng7 e5 koh long2 si7 siok8 pak-hng e5 Thai3-ia5-chok8; chit8 e5 si7 hu7-jin5-lang5 kio3-cho3 Chi-oang2, i e5 mou7-hiam2 ti7 chin3-cheng5 i2-keng kong2-khi2 liau2; koh chit8 e5 chiu7-si7 siau3-lian5 lang5 kio3-cho3 Lou5-ui, Ti7 chian3-cheng tiong bat siu7 koaiN-kaN. Lou5-ui bat siu7 koe3 chin kek-liat8 e5 phaiN2 khoan2-thai7. I e5 kou3-su7 khah ban7 beh lai5 kong2-khi2. Ia7 chit ui7 Chi-oang2 tau3-ti2 si7 sim2-mih8 khoan2 leh? I sui-jian5 si7 bo5 hak8-bun7, sin-the2 lam2-lam2, iau2-ku2 khak-sit8 lai5 kong2, i m7-si7 loan2-jiok8 e5 lang5. Tui3 i e5 gan2-lai7 u7 hian2-chhut chit8 chiong2 put-kho2 bu2-jiok8 e5 cheng-sin5, ia7 chit chiong2 cheng-sin5 u7 chiam3-leng2 i e5 choan5 jin5-keh, hou7 kiN3-na7 oa2-lai5 chiu7-kun7 i e5 lang5 long2 siu7-tioh8 i e5 kam2-hoa3. Lian5 Jit8-pun2 lang5 ia7 khoaN3 i chin u7 khi2, na7-si7 in ka-ki7 e5 lang5 si7 jin7 i cho3 sin5-leng5 e5 lau7-bu2; eng7 boe7-oe7 hoa-khi3 e5 khian5-seng5 teh thiaN3 i. Li2 na7 thak8 koh soa3--loh8-khi3 chit chiuN, chiu7-si7 choan-kang beh kong2-khi2 i e5 li2-lek8 e5 chit8 chiuN. Li2 kiam2-chhai2 choe3-chio2 iah8 beh tong5-i3 kong2, I si7 choe3 tu3-mia5 e5 hu7-lu2 e5 chit8-e5; chiu7-si7 Siong7-te3 sou2 eng7 lai5 oan5-seng5 I hit e5 ui2-tai7 koh ko-siong7 e5 chi2-i3 e5. 
  Ho5-peng5 e5 chhe-sai3--Chi-oang2 
  1895 ni5, te7-it chhu3 Tiong Jit8 chian3-cheng au7, kun-ku3 Ma2-koan tiau5-iok e5 tiau5-kiaN7, Tiong-kok siu7 pek, kou-put-chiong tioh8 chiong Tai5-oan5 jiong7-tou7 hou7 Jit8-pun2. Chong2-si7 Tai5-oan5 e5 peh-siN3 ku7-choat8, m7 seng5-jin7 chit e5 tiau5-iok; chiu7 soan-pou3 Tai5-oan5 cho3 tok8-lip8 e5 kiong7-ho5 kok. Ui7-tioh8 an2-ni, Jit8-pun2 e5 hai2-kun chiu7 chek-si5 tui3 pak-pou7 siong7-liok8, hit e5 te7-hng cheng3-koan5 chiu7 ti7 iu-se3 e5 bu2-lek8 e5 bin7-cheng5 liam5-piN khui-hoe khi3. Chi2-u7 koan5-soaN e5 goan5 chu7-bin5 u7 ho2-taN2 kap i ti2-khong3, ke3-siok8 kap i chian3 kui2-na7 ni5. Khi2-chhou Jit8-pun2 lang5 chin bo5 eng5, mi5-jit8 eng7 sim ti7 siat lut8-le7 kap hoat-leng7, thang lai5 ti7-li2 hiah-e5 khia7-khi2 ti7 sai-pou7 piN5-iuN5 e5 Tai5-oan5 lang5; chiu7 bo5 sim-chiaN5 thang koan2-kou3 soaN-te7, i2-kip8 kai2-koat hiah-e5 chhu2 lang5-thau5-khak--e5. Kau3 in he7 kha-chhiu2 chou2-chit tho2-hoat8-tui7 beh khi3 tho2-hoat8 in e5 si5, chiah chai-iaN2 beh cheng-hok8 in m7-si7 iong5-iN7, u7 i3-goa7 e5 hi-seng kap kan-lan5 ti7-teh. In e5 iu5-kek-tui7 bih ti7 am7 e5 chhiu7-na5 lai7, i2-kip8 chhim e5 soaN-giam5-nih, ti7-chia ti7-hia thau phah Jit8-pun2 kun, hou7 in lap8 liau2 tang7-tang7 e5 hiat-soe3. Chiah-e5 lang5 chu7-jian5 si7 chin m7 hoaN-hi2 jim7-ho5 e5 bu2-chong pou7-tui7 lai5 chhim-liok8 in e5 soaN-che7; in-ui7 in liah8 hiah-e5 soaN-che7 cho3 si7 in e5 tek8-iu2 chai5-san2. In siong5-siong5 khoaN3 hiah-e5 khia7-khi2 ti7 piN5-iuN5 e5 Tai5-oan5 lang5 si7 lau3-sai2-be2--e5, in-ui7 tu3 bo5 saN-e7 pou2-thau5 chiu7 liam5-piN un--loh8-khi3. Tok8-tok8 in chiah si7 ai3-houN3 chu7-iu5 e5 koan5-soaN teng2 e5 chu7-bin5, iah8 chiu3-choa7 m7 tau5-hang5. 
  Iu5-kek chian3 ke3-siok8 chap8 ni5 ku2, ti7 hit e5 khun3-lan5 e5 soaN-te7-nih, u7-si5 thai5, u7-si5 hioh; au7-lai5 hit e5 chong-pi7 iu-siu3 e5 Jit8-pun2-kun u7 chiam7-chiam7 tit8-tioh8 iu2-li7 e5 te7-pou7. Jit8-pun2 lang5 ui7-tioh8 koaN2-kin2 beh ti7 ko-san-chok8 e5 te7-kai3 lai5 chhai2-hoat8 chiuN-lo2 soaN i2-kip8 kiN5-thaN choe7-choe7 po2-kui3 e5 bok8-chhai5. Chiu7 chun2-pi7 beh kap chiah-e5 u7 ke3-tat8 e5 tek8-jin5─Thai3-ia5-chok8, Bu2-lun2-chok8, i2-kip8 Pai5-oan-chok8─lai5 teng3-lip8 chit8 e5 bo5 sit the2-bian7 e5 ho5-iok. Jit8-pun2-kun kap chiah-e5 hoan-sia7 teh chian3 e5 si5, cham2-jian5 u7 hi-seng, u7 sit-loh8 kui2-na7 e5 pou7-tui7. Chiu7 chiong ko-san-chok8 e5 iau3-sai3 eng7 tian7-soaN3 ka7 i ui5--khi2-lai5, pang3 hou7 in khi3 kou-lip8. 
  In e5 boat8-lou7 si7 boe7 bian2-tit e5. Hoan-sia7 chit8-sia7 koe3 chit8-sia7 tit8-tit8 hang5--khi3, soa3 kap in kang2-ho5; chi2-u7 chhun chit8 ui7 iong2-beng2 e5 Thai3-lou2-kok sia7 (Thai3-ia5 chok8 e5 chit8 sia7) kian-siu2 m7-goan5 hang5. In e5 tin7-te7 si7 siat ti7 Thai3-lou2-kok soaN-giam5 teng2 hiam2-iau3 e5 chioh8-tong7-nih, in u7 chiam3-ku3 chit8 jiah thian-jian5 e5 chhiu7-na5, si7 Jit8-pun2 kun bo5 hoat-tou7 thang sip8-kek e5; sui-bong2 si7 an2-ni, in kau3 be2 iah8 si7 tioh8 hang5, na7 bo5 chiu7 go7-si2. Au7-lai5 jit8-chi2 i2-keng kau3, Thai3-ia5 chok8 e5 thau5-lang5 chiu7 kam2-kak tioh8 kong2 in e5 khui3-lat8 i2-keng chhiong-hun tit-tioh8 cheng3-beng5 lah, na7 ke3-siok8 koh thai5 loh8-khi3, an2-ni sng3 m7-si7 chhong-beng5; siuN7 kong2 ti7 hit e5 si5-chun7 lai5 kang2-ho5 iah8 i2-keng m7-si7 kian3-siau3 e5 su7 lah. In-ui7 “U7-si5 thang thai5-lang5, u7-si5 thang i-ti7, u7-si5 thang kau-chian3, u7-si5 thang ho5-ho2.” Kiam2 bo5 sim2-mih8 ta-pou-lang5 a2-si7 hu7-jin5-lang5 thang ui7-tioh8 in lai5 kap tui3-tek8 teng3-lip8 chit8 e5 kong-eng5 e5 ho5-iok mah? Chi7-chui7 beh chhut-thau5 lai5 tam-tng in e5 thong-ek8 i2-kip8 tiau-kai2-chia2 e5 chit-bu7 ah? Chiong3-gi7 it koat, chiu7 tui3 in ka-ki7 e5 peh-siN3 e5 tiong-kan soan2-chhut chit8 ui7 hu7-jin5-lang5 kio3 cho3 Chi-oang2, si7 36 hoe3 lang5. I bat kap chit8 e5 Tai5-oan5 e5 seng-li2 lang5 kiat-hun, ia7 khia7-khi2 ti7 tang-hai2-hoaN7 e5 Hoe-lian5-kang2. I bat Jit8-pun2 oe7, iah8 oe7 kong2 chin liu5-li7 e5 Tai5-oan5 oe7 kah na2 chhin-chhiuN7 kong2 in ka-ki7 e5 Thai3-ia5 oe7 chit8-iuN7. Tui3 pat8 hong-bin7 lai5 kong2, i ia7 si7 chit8 ui7 phoaN3-toan3-lek8 kian7-choan5 e5 ti3-sek hu7-lu2, chin u7 koan-sim ti7 i e5 tong5-pau e5 li7-hai7 koan-he7. Tui3 i e5 gau5 chiu-soan5, ti7 Jit8-pun2 kun kap Thai3-ia5-chok8 e5 tiong-kan ko2-jian5 seng5-lip8 liau2 chit8 e5 liong2-hong moa2-i3 e5 ho5-iok. Tui3 hit-tiap8 i2-au7, Chi-oang2 chit e5 mia5-ji7 chiu7 tauh8-tauh8 hou7 lang5 khoaN3 chin u7 khi2. Jit8-pun2 e5 tong-kiok8-chia2 ui7-tioh8 i e5 kong3-hian3 m7-bat bo5 tui3 i piau2-si7 kam2-liam7 e5 i3-su3; iah8 hou7 i pi2 pat8 lang5 khah u7 heng5-tong7 chu7-iu5 e5 koan5, pat8 lang5 beh ti7-hia chhut-jip8 tioh8 siu7 keng2-chhat e5 hu2-kho2, na7 si7 i chiu7 m7-bian2. I bo5-lun7 kau3 sim2-mih8 sou2-chai7, lang5 to long2 bat i chiu7-si7 hit ui7 cho7-chiu7 ho5-peng5 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5, si7 “Ho5-peng5 e5 chhe-sai3 Chi-oang2.” Ji7-chap8 ni5 au7, si5-kan teh-beh kau3, i beh siu7 tiau3 lai5 cho3 hit e5 oat8-ju2 koh-khah ko-siong7 e5 kang, chiu7-si7 in2-chhoa7 lang5 kap Siong7-te3 ho5-ho2 e5 kang. 
  TaN chit e5 Chi-oang2 tau3-ti2 si7 ui7-tioh8 sim2-mih8 in-toaN, ia7 ti7 sim2-mih8 si5-chun7 thau5 chit8 pai2 lai5 chiap-chhiok-tioh8 sin3-giong2? Che khiok si7 bo5 lang5 chai-iaN2, put-ko3 sou2 chai-iaN2 chit8 hang7, chiu7-si7 na7 m7-si7 i e5 tiong7-hu, chiu7-si7 i e5 ta-ke u7 chiaN5-cho3 jiat8-sim e5 Ki-tok-tou5. I e5 ta-ke ti7 Chiong-hoa3 Ki-tok-kau3 piN7-iN7 cho3 hoan7-chia2 e5 si5, thau5 chit8 pai2 thiaN-tioh8 to7-li2. Ka-na2-tai7 TiuN2-lo2-hoe7 thoe3-jim7 e5 soan-kau3-su Liat8 Kou-niu5 bat ti7 Tai5-oan5 cho3 kang choe7-choe7 ni5. I kong2 i ti7 1929 ni5, u7 khi3 Tai5-tiong te7-hng hong2-bun7 chit8 keng toa7-toa7 keng e5 long5-ka, ti7-hia u7 tu2-tioh8 chit8 ui7 lau7 hu7-jin5-lang5, chiu7-si7 chiong5-chian5 bat ti7 Lan5 I-seng hia thiaN-tioh8 to7-li2 e5. I e5 to7-li2 kiam2-chhai2 bat bo5 kah loa7 chhim, m7-ku2 ti7 sou2 bat e5 hoan7-ui5 lai7 chin kian-kou3 sin3. Hit jit8 i e5 sim-pu7 Chi-oang2 u7 che7 ti7 i e5 bin5-chhng5 piN, in saN-kap eng7 chit8 khoan2 hi-ki5 e5 ko-san tiau7 teh gim5 Seng3-si te7-it siu2 “Siong7-te3 chhong3-cho7 thiN kap toe7.” Leng7-goa7 koh chit8 pai2, Liat8 Kou-niu5 u7 ti7 chit8 ui7 Ko-san-chok8 e5 lu2-chu2 e5 ke-nih tu2-tioh8 Chi-oang2, hit ui7 lu2-chu2 kio3 cho3 Siu3-li2, chiong5-chian5 bat ti7 Tam7-chui2 thak8-chheh. Liat8 Kou-niu5 chiu7 siuN7 beh khoan3-iu2 Chi-oang2 khi3 Tam7-chui2 thak8 Seng3-keng hak8-hau7. 
  Ka-na2-tai7 TiuN2-lo2-hoe7 e5 soan-kau3-su Sun Nga2-kok Bok8-su ti7 1929 ni5, iah8 bat tu2-tioh8 Chi-oang2. Hit-chun7 chiau3 i sou2 khoaN3, i si7 chit8 ui7 “tiong-lo2 i2-siong7 loan2-jiok8 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5” (hit-chun7 si7 58 hoe3), ti7 i e5 bin7-nih u7 chhiah Thai3-ia5-chok8 tok8-iu2 e5 hoe-ji7 ti7-teh. (Thai3-ia5-chok8 long2 u7 chhiah hoe-ji7 ti7 in e5 thau5-hiah8-nih; kiat-hun liau2 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 iah8 u7 chhiah, chiu7-si7 tui3 chhui3-kak kap chhui3-e7-tau2 tit8 chhiah thau3 kau3 hi7-a2 piN). Sun Bok8-su thau5-chit8 pai2 sou2 tu2-tioh8 e7-hiau2 kong2 Tai5-oan5 oe7 e5 ko-san-chok8 chiu7-si7 i. I chiu7 khoan3-iu2 i khi3 Tam7-chui2 thak8 Seng3-keng hak8-hau7, chong2-si7 i u7 tiu5-tu5 m7-kaN2 khi3. I chin ai3 lai5, chong2-si7 i kiam2-boe7 siuN choe7 hoe3? Lang5 ni5-ki2 chiah-nih8 lau7, chiah beh koh lai5 thak8 chiah-e5 chheh, an2-ni kiam2 u7 siaN2 lou7-eng7? Iu7-koh kam2-kak-tioh8 ka-ki7 e5 bin7-nih u7 chhiah hoe7-ji7, chhiah kau3 hoe-li2 hoe-lo, na7 ti7 cheng3 hak8-seng e5 tiong-kan un2-tang3 kam2-kak kou-tok8, ka-ki7 chit8 e5 bo5-lam7 bo5-lam7. Sui-bong2 si7 an2-ni, i chiu7 koat-sim beh khi3, chiu7 kap Sun Sian-siN cho3 phoaN7, khi3 Tam7-chui2; ti7-hia phian-jip8 Seng3-keng hak8-hau7, thak8-chheh nng7 ni5 ku2. 
  U7 lang5 gi7-lun7 kong2, Iong5-un2 chit khoan2 poe3-keng2 ki5-iN7 jin5-but8 kap lang5 bo5 kang7 khoan2 e5 hak8-seng ti7-hia thak8-chheh, tau3-ti2 si7 sim2-mih8 ti3-hui7? Put-tan3 an2-ni, i e5 sin-khu koh bo5 kah loa7 iong2, chiau3 khoaN3 beh oan5-seng5 i e5 hak8-giap8 si7 chin lan5-tit e5 khoan2. Na7-si7 Seng3 Sin5 e5 lat8 u7 chhiong-moa2-tioh8 i hit e5 loan2-jiok8 e5 the2-keh, chiu7 li7-khui(pit-giap8) hit keng hak8-hau7, “ti7 Chu2 e5 oe7 iong2-chong3,” eng7 thiam5-cheng7 e5 sin3-sim lai5 soan-thoan5 Siong7-te3 sou2 kau-thok i e5 oe7. 
  1931 ni5, i chiu7 tng2-khi3 tang-hai2-hoaN7, cheng7-cheng7 lai5 khai-si2 i e5 kang-chok. I u7 ti7 Thai3-ia5-chok8 e5 hiuN-sia7-nih lai5 ka3-si7 ko3-jin5 kap sio2 thoan5-the2 e5 lang5. Jit8-pun2 e5 keng2-chhat u7 tham3-thiaN-tioh8 i e5 hoat8-tong7, iah8 iau-kiu5 in tioh8 tiong-chi2. TaN, kong-khai e5 chu7-hoe7 ki3-jian5 si7 gui5-hiam2, i chiu7 ti7 pi3-bit8 e5 tiong-kan lai5 chu7-hoe7. Keng2-chhat chiu7 chin bit8-chhiat lai5 kam3-si7 i e5 heng5-tong7, hou7 i bo5 pan7-hoat thang chit8-sia7 iu5 koe3 chit8-sia7. Su7-cheng5 sui-jian5 piN3 kau3 an2-ni, i iah8 eng7 hoat-tou7, eng7 me5-si5 lai5 chiu-ui5 e5 kok sou2-chai7 chhut-sek8 pi3-bit8 e5 chu7-hoe7. I khia7-khi2 ti7 Ka-le2-oan2, chiu7-si7 tu2-tu2 ti7 Hoe-lian5-kang2 pak-si3 e5 piN5-iuN5 (khoaN3 te7-tou5), peh-siN3 tui3 hng7-kin7 e5 sou2-chai7 lai5 chiu7-kun7 i e5 ka3-si7; hit e5 siau3-giah8 u7 jit8-jit8 teh ke-thiN. Mui2-pai2 keng2-chhat e5 kam3-si7 na7 khah leng-khi3 e5 si5, i chiu7 liu--chhut-lai5, sun7 hoe2-chhia-lou7 loh8 lam5 khi3 cho3 hit e5 “Siong7-teng2-siong7 e5 kang.” I put-lun7 khi3 sim2-mih8 sou2-chai7, eng2 u7 cho7-chiu7 chit8-koa2 sin3-chia2, in tiong-kan choe7-choe7 lang5 u7 ke3-siok8 khi3 Ka-le2-oan2 chhoe7 i, lai5 hak8-sip8 hok-im khah siong5-se3. I e5 chhu3 chiu7 piN3-chiaN5 kek-le7 tong5-chi3 e5 chhu3. Choe7-choe7 Ki-tok-tou5 e5 siu2-leng2 kap kang-lang5 u7 ti7-hia kap hiah-e5 tui3 tang-hai2-hoaN7 e5 lam5-pak ji7-lou7 chip8-oa2-lai5 e5 Ki-tok-tou5 siong-hoe7. I e5 hak8-seng tai7-ke u7 chit8 hang7 e5 kiong7-thong tiam2, chiu7-si7 lang5-lang5 tioh8 tng2-khi3 thoan5 hok-im hou7 pat8 lang5, soa3 in2-chhoa7 in lai5 kui Ki-tok. In tiong-kan toa7-poaN3 e5 lang5 long2 u7 hu7-chek tioh8 kian3-siat in ka-ki7 e5 kau3-hoe7. In iau2 u7 leng7-goa7 chit8 hang7 e5 kiong7-thong tiam2, chiu7-si7 siu7 keng2-chhat e5 oan3-hun7 kap hoan2-tui3. In tioh8 khi3 kian3-siat in e5 kau3-hoe7, chiu7-si7 u7 pi3-bit8 e5 hoe7-iu2 e5; chiah-e5 hoe7-iu2 na7 siu7 hoat-kian3-tioh8 e5 si5, tai7-ke tioh8 ui7-tioh8 sin3-giong2 chin chiah8-khou2. Ti7 teng2-chiuN sou2 kong2 e5 Sam-lip8-san, i2-kip8 ki5-u5 nng7 e5 kau3-hoe7, chiu7-si7 an2-ni seng5-lip8--e5. 
  Chi-oang2 tui3 Sam-lip8-san thoat-hiam2 e5 su7 u7 kek-khi2 keng2-chhat e5 siu7-khi3, sou2-i2 in chiu7 chiong in e5 siu7-khi3 chhian kau3 ti7-hia e5 Ki-tok-tou5 e5 sin-chiuN7. In chiu7 but8-siu in e5 Seng3-keng kap Seng3-si pang3-hoe2 sio. U7 kui2-na7 e5 sin3-tou5 hou7 in leng5-ti7, iah8 hou7 in phah, phah kau3 phiN7-khang-huih siang-kang2 to3. In iah8 sai in e5 thau5-khak, cheng in e5 hi7-a2 bong, hou7 in piN3-chiaN5 chhau3-hi7-lang5 kui2-na7-jit8 ku2 boe7 thiaN-kiN3. In tiong-kan u7 chit8 e5 chit-bun7 keng2-chhat, kong2, “Lin2 siaN2-su7 khoan2-thai7 goan2 an2-ni?” Keng2-chhat in3 i kong2, “In-ui7 lin2 sin3 Bi2-kok lang5 e5 Siong7-te3.” In chiu7 chu2-tiuN kong2, “I m7-si7 Bi2-kok lang5 e5 Siong7-te3; I si7 choan5 se3-kai3 e5 lang5 e5 Siong7-te3.” Keng2-chhat chhiu2 ki2 sin5-sia7 po3 in khoaN3, kong2, “Lin2 khoaN3-mai7! hit e5 chiah si7 lan2 e5 sin5-beng5.” Ti7 hit-chun7 hiah-e5 sin3-tou5 u7 chit8 e5 chin ho2-taN2, ka7 i kong2, “Hiah-e5 na7-si7 sin5-beng5 lai5 kong2, in thai2 boe7 in2-chhoa7 lin2 kiaN5 si3-chiaN3 e5 lou7?” Keng2-chhat siu7-khi3 toa7 siaN hoah kong2, “Li2 teh kong2 siaN2?” Hit ui7 sin3-tou5 chiu7 eng7 tim5-tiok8 e5 thai3-tou7, ki2 sit8-le7 soat-beng5 kong2, “Ti7 lin2 e5 Jit8-pun2 kau3-oan5 e5 tiong-kan u7 chit8 e5 heng5-ui5 bo5 su3-cheng3, iau2-ku2 i iah8 teh pai3......” Keng2-chhat toa7 siaN hoah kong2, “Bian2 kong2! tiam7-tiam7 ho2, ...... lin2 kin-a2-jit8 bu2-jiok8 goan2 chin thiam2.” Au7-lai5 hiah-e5 sin3-tou5 u7 siu7 khong3-sou3, “in-ui7 in u7 khah heng3-su7 tam7-poh8, kong2-oe7 u7 khan-gai7-tioh8 kau3-iok8 e5 bun7-te5.” 
  Chhin-chhiuN7 chit ho7 e5 pek-hai7 (che si7 chin-che7 pai2 e5) na7 hou7 Chi-oang2 thiaN-tioh8 e5 si5, i chiu7 toa7-toa7 chhau-sim peh-pak. I iah8 u7 keng-giam7-tioh8 seng3 Po2-lo5 sou2 kong2 e5 oe7, “U7 chit8 e5 tang7-taN3 jit8-jit8 teh teh goa2 e5, chiu7-si7 thoe3 cheng3 kau3-hoe7 iu-bun7 e5 su7.” I khak-sit8 chin i3-ai3 i sou2 in2-chhoa7 lai5 jip8 sin3-giong2 e5 lang5 long2 tiong2-toa7 ti7 chin-li2 e5 ti3-hui7, iah8 chiaN5-choe3 iong2-chong3 thang lai5 jim2-siu7 khou2-lan7. I put-si5 put-khek chin tioh8-boa5, ng3-bang7 in ti7 Seng3-keng oe7 thang tit-tioh8 chhiong-hun e5 ka3-si7, thang lai5 hu5-hap8 ti7 in sou2 u7 e5 ng3-bang7. 
  Chian3-cheng au7 keng-koe3 liau2 kui2-na7 ni5, Sun Sian-siN u7 khi3 Hoe-lian5-kang2 pak-si3 e5 te7-thau5 soaN-kia7 koan5-koan5 e5 sou2-chai7, hong2-bun7 chit8 ui7 sio2 hiuN-sia7 kio3-cho3 Gu7-khu-chuh (Gukutsu). I ti7-hia u7 khoaN3-tioh8 chit8 keng chin toa7-keng e5 kau3-hoe7, iah8 oe7 thang kap Iap8 In7-to5 tam5-lun7 choe7-choe7 e5 tai7-chi3; chit e5 lang5 ti7 in2-chhoa7 hit chng-nih e5 lang5 lai5 sin3 Chu2 e5 su7, u7 chin toa7 e5 kong3-hian3 ti7-teh. 
  Sun Sian-siN mng7 i kong2, “Li2 ti7 khi2-chhou si7 an2-choaN2-iuN7 tit-tioh8 hok-im leh?” In3 kong2, “Goa2 tit-tioh8 hok-im si7 tui3 goa2 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 e5 chi2-moe7; i ti7 1942 ni5, u7 tui3 Thai3-lou2-kok e5 sou2-chai7 lai5 goa2 chia.” I ui7-tioh8 ai3 bat khah siong5-se3, chiu7 lek8-koe3 kui2-na7 le2-pai3 ku2 e5 lou7-theng5 khi3 Chi-oang2 hia, tui3 i hak8-sip8. Chit e5 lou7-theng5 saN-li7 iok 20 eng-li2. I tioh8 ti7 mi5-si5 khi3, kau3 ui7 kap i hak8-sip8 nng7-tiam2 a2-si7 saN-tiam2 cheng ku2, chiu7 to3-tng2--lai5, tioh8 ti7 thiN boe7 kng e5 si5 kau3 chhu3. 
  Iap8 In7-to5 eng7 chhim-tim5 e5 thai3-tou7 kong2, “Chi-oang2 ka7 goa2 kong2, Tng I iau2-be7 chiong to7-li2 ka3-si7 goa2 kau3 chin tho3-tong3 e5 si5, kah goa2 m7-thang ui7-tioh8 beh tit-tioh8 lang5 lai5 tui3 lang5 kong2 to7-li2.” 
  Sun Sian-siN mng7 i kong2, “I ka3 li2 loa7 ku2?” 
  In3 kong2, “SaN ko3-geh8.” 
  Koh mng7 i kong2, “Li2 u7 theng3-hau7 sou2 kong2 e5 ki5-kan kau3, chiah chhut-khi3 cho3 kang a2-bo5?” 
  I kong2, “He2 bo5 nou3, goa2 ia7 oe7 thang theng3-hau7 kau3 hiah ku2; si5-kan boe7 kau3, goa2 tioh8 tui3 kui2-na7 lang5 kong2 to7-li2 lah.” 
  “Tng i teh ka3-si7 li2 e5 ki5-kan iau2-boe7 kiat-sok e5 si5, li2 tit-tioh8 loa7-choe7 lang5?” I in3 kong2, “Gou7 khau2-chau3.” 
  I boe7 tan2-tit kau3, ki5-kan kau3 chiah tui3 lang5 kong2 to7-li2! Iah8 ti7 teh siu7 hun3-lian7 e5 saN ko3-geh8 kan i u7 tit-tioh8 25 lang5. Au7-lai5 keng2-chhat u7 hoat-kian3-tioh8 i teh khui pi3-bit8 e5 chu7-hoe7, chiu7 hou7 i siu7-tioh8 chin e7 kiaN lang5 e5 pek-hai7. 
  Chong2-si7 chit ui7 Chi-oang2 cho3 ko-san-chok8 Ki-tok-tou5 e5 leng2-siu3, i pun2-sin m7-bat hou7 keng2-chhat liah8-khi3, soa3 koaiN-loh8 kaN; che tau3-ti2 si7 sim2-mih8 ian5-kou3? Tui3 chit e5 bun7-toe5 e5 kai2-tap, lan2 khah toa7 bin7 thang an2-ni kong2, ‘Siat-su2 in na7 kaN2 liah8 i, in khak-sit8 oe7 thang liah8 i.’ Hou7 keng2-chhat m7-kaN2 sui5-pian7 mou7-hiam2 lai5 tui3 lang5 cho3 chhut kek8-toan e5 heng5-ui5 e5, chit ui7 Chi-oang2 chiu7-si7 i5-it e5 ho2 le7. Te7-hng e5 keng2-chhat kap sio2-koaN kiam2-chhai2 khi3 kau3 phut-phut-thiau3, iah8 eng7 koe3 choe7-choe7 chiong2 e5 heng5-hoat8 lai5 haN2 i, m7-ku2 hiah-e5 pi2-kau3-tek khah toa7 e5 koaN-li7 si7 kau3-giah8 chai-iaN2, siat-su2 in na7 sun2-hai7 i chit8 ki e5 thau5-mng5, chiu7 Thai3-ia5-chok8 choan5-chok8 kiam2-chhai2 oe7 khi2 hoan2-loan7; in-ui7 in eng2 bo5 boe7 ki3-tit i ui7-tioh8 in sou2 kian3-lip8 hian2-tu3 e5 kong-lou5; ia7 choe7-choe7 lang5 un2-tang3 kam-goan7 ui7-tioh8 i lai5 hi-seng in e5 siN3-mia7. Kiam2-chhai2 thang kong2, Jit8-pun2 lang5 iah8 m7-si7 bong5-un poe7-gi7 e5, ui7-tioh8 an2-ni, chiah sin7-tiong7 bo5 phaiN2 khoan2-thai7 i. Chong2-kong2, Ti7 chian3-si5 kek8 khun3-lan5 e5 kui2 ni5 tiong, i u7 si3-koe3 kiaN5 bo5 tai7-chi3, ti7 i loan2-jiok8 e5 sin-the2 sou2 oe7 iong5-un2-tit e5 hoan7-ui5-lai7, chin3-heng5 kau3-hoe7 e5 kang-chok. 
  I ti7 1946 ni5 e5 chhun-thiN li7-khui se3-kan, hiong2-siu7 74 hoe3. I li7-khui se3-kan nng7 ko3-geh8 au7, Sun Sian-siN u7 khi3 Hoe-lian5-kang2 Ki-tok-kau3 kong-thiong2-nih khoaN3 i e5 bong7, ti7-hia i khoaN3-tioh8 Thai3-ia5-chok8 e5 Ki-tok-tou5 u7 kian3-cho7 chit8 te3 gou7-chhioh koan5 e5 chioh8-pi, teng2-bin7 koa3 chit8 ki toa7-toa7 ki e5 sip8-ji7-ke3 teh ki3-liam7 i. I u7 an2-ni sia2 kong2, “Chit e5 bong7 chin-chiaN3 si7 sin5-seng3 e5 sou2-chai7; in-ui7 kang2-chheng lang5 u7 jin7 i cho3 in e5 sin5-leng5 e5 lau7-bu2. Siong7-te3 eng7 chit e5 lang5 ti7 chiah-ni7 te2 e5 ki5-kan lai5 oan5-seng5 chiah-ni7 choe7 e5 tai7-chi3, che chai7 Tai5-oan5 si7 long2 bo5, chai7 pat8-ui7 iah8 si7 han2-tit u7 e5.” 
  Lan2 ia7 thang chai 1945 ni5 9 geh8, Jit8-pun2 tau5-hang5 e5 si5 i iau2 ti7-teh. Chit8-e7 thiaN-kiN3 i sou2 thiaN3 e5 tong5-pau tit-tioh8 kai2-hong3, m7-bian2 koh siu7 pek-hai7, i e5 hoaN-hi2 kau3 chaiN2-iuN7! Kui2-na7 ni5 ku2 i u7 thoe3 in ki5-to2, eng7 chin-li2 lai5 ka3-si7 in, eng7 sin3-giong2 kap iong2-khi3 lai5 kou2-le7 in, hou7 in oe7-tit-thang jim2-siu7 hoan7-lan7, chiok-hok in, in-ui7 in i2-keng jip8 ti7 sin3-kau3 chu7-iu5 e5 sin si5-tai7; na7-si7 i pun2-sin khiok i2-keng jip8 ti7 Chu2 e5 khoai3-lok8. 
